a.title: Retrieve the current version of the dashboard. This could take a long time!

svg:desc.p: The graphical version of this page shows an overview of the work in progress on the magnet and QRL slots in the LHC.

p.strong: To see the image, you have to install either Firefox or an Internet Explorer plugin.

svg:desc.p: Technical explanation: MTF fetches the current status information for all the jobs on all the magnet and QRL slots every time this page is loaded, and generates a graphical view of this dynamically, using the XML based vector graphics language SVG. Mozilla Firefox version 1.5 supports SVG natively, while a plugin for Internet Explorer 6.0 is available from Adobe.
